name: com.android.voicemail.impl.scheduling.TaskReceiver
description: BroadcastReceiver to queue and run Task with the android.app.job.JobScheduler. A task is queued using a explicit broadcast to this receiver. The intent should contain enough information in Intent#getExtras() to construct the task (see Tasks#createIntent(Context, Class)). The task will be queued directly in TaskExecutor if it is already running, or in TaskSchedulerJobService if not.
